Description: Blue glazed composition amulet in the form of a falcon-headed crocodile wearing the sun-disc; suspension ring beneath the beak.
Curator's comments: Published: Andrews, Amulets of Ancient Egypt (1994): fig.41 Quack, J.F. 2022. Altägyptische Amulette und ihre Handhabung. Orientalische Religionen in der Antike 31. Tübingen, p. 241.
